## 6. Canvas Button Fix

Previous issue:

> 所有功能鍵按了後都沒反應。

Cause:

JavaScript strings contained raw line breaks inside `confirm()` or `log()`, causing browser script parsing to fail.

Fixed format:

```javascript
confirm("防呆確認：刪除隔離檔案\n\n確定要徹底刪除隔離紀錄嗎？")
```

Validation:

```text
Node JS syntax check returncode = 0
Node JS syntax stdout = OK
```

